Dialogs.Dialog: I'm on my way somewhere, so I'm in a hurry.
I see. Sorry for stopping you.
With such a pick up line, I thought...
(That's ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Did she have a shift today？)
Did you have a shift today？
No. Someone couldn't make it so I came in.
Hehe. Then it would help if you support me.
Okay. If you are all right with me.
(It's not what I need to worry about.)
(Oh, how was I supposed to do this...？)
Um, how am I supposed to do this...？
You're welcome. Keep learning it a little at a time.
Got it. I'll do my best.
Ah, don't you need to go soon？
▲主人公＊▲. I'm doing an errand for a teacher.
Is there anything I can help you with？
No, it's not a big deal.
We talked for quite a bit. I guess I'll get going.
Yeah？ Then I guess I'll get going too.
Ah, I have to get going.
That's right. Sorry for stopping you.
(That's right. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is taking a break, too. She might be in the break room now.)
(Well, whatever. I'll get some fresh air outside.)
No, I just think that we both are taking breaks at the same time.
It's about time for me to go back.
(I should also go back to work soon...)
Aren't you looking a bit tired？
The customers will settle down soon, so do your best. Okay？
(All right！ I'll work hard for a bit more.)
▲主人公＊▲. What's up？ You don't seem very energetic.
Really？ I'm hungry, so maybe that's why.
Hehe, just like a boy. Then I'll give you something good. Keep it a secret from the teacher.
A cough drop. It might not help your hunger much though.
(Yeah, I think it helped a bit.)
Hehe, just kidding. I was teasing you.
Ah, I have to get going. See you later.
Not really. I saw you from afar, so I tried to call you.
Ah, I'm sorry. I stopped you and kept you occupy. I guess I'll be going now.
I had a good time chatting with you.
Seems like we can see each other everywhere. When I see you around, I... No, never mind. See you later.
Hehe, just kidding. Did it surprise you？
We've been talking for a while.
Yeah. I've got to go now. Bye-bye.
Ahaha. You were surprised. So cute▼
Oh, don't do that to me.
But teasing you is fun. I've got something to do, so I have to get going. Bye-bye.
(She left... Somehow, she seemed to enjoy teasing me...)
Eh？ Are you working？ You're taking a break？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ has a lot to take care of. I'll help you then.
See？ When we did this together, we could get it done faster.
Thank you. Sorry for making you work during your break.
I think I need your help.
Okay but you have to ask me nicely.
(So many customers today. I guess I won't have time for a break.)
It's your break time, right？ You should rest.
But it's so crowded like this...
Just be obedient. Break time is break time. Go.
Okay. I got it. Thank you.
(Even now, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is still taking care of me...)
Is there anything you want？ Why didn't you just come in？
Well, it might not be good if a student of higher grade get in the classroom.
You don't have to worry about that.
Ah, class is about to start.
Sorry. I've been here until the bell rang. I've got to go.
Don't worry about that. It's okay.
(I feel like someone is staring at me...)
I'm here. You're great to notice that I'm here.
I have to go. I'll drop by again, I guess.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What's the matter？ Why did you come to my class？
Of course, I want to see you.
Okay, I have to go. I'll drop by again.
I'm thinking that there aren't any people around.
You know that I can't refuse.
I'm thinking that there aren't any people around.
Yes... But don't get carried away, okay？
I'm thinking that there aren't any people around.
Okay, now it's enough. All right？
I think you already know that this is special just for today, okay？
Hey. We are at work now...
But we can do it, right？
Just don't forget that we're at work now, okay？
Do you think this is okay？
No！ What if someone came here？
You're getting carried away again. Geez.
Let's stop it before someone's here.
This is special just for this time. Really.
